data.description: Charming 2bed, 1.5 bath condo located in the Venetian Condominiums. This well-maintained unit offers a spacious living with open area, updated kitchen with modern appliances, and a private balcony with scenic views. Enjoy the convenience of in-unit laundry and reserved parking. The gated community features a pool, community room, fitness center, wine cellar, and is nestled in a serene neighborhood. Close proximity to parks, shops, and dining. Perfect for a cozy and convenient lifestyle.
